                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The greater hellcat is critically hit by any Strike</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The greater hellcat's Menacing Growl recharges. The creature that dealt the triggering Strike must succeed at a @Check[will|dc:37] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 4} on a critical failure).</p>"
                },
