                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The greater hellcat Strides and makes a Strike at the end of that movement. If the greater hellcat began this action @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Hidden], it remains hidden until after the ability's Strike.</p>"
